{"tid":1540776,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高志森：建議香港記者證由警署發出","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T12:58:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":37,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"df423cd565cc2915168bce12651218d857b6c5a8","tid":1540776,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"早前導演高志森因為在Facebook張貼極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）的照片，而被封鎖帳戶3日，更於微博求救：「希望有百萬網軍為我出氣、平反」。高志森昨晚再於Facebook貼出一張自製並用簡體字寫上《曱甴大戰》的海報，再留言呼籲萬人投書，「強烈要求取消香港記者協會的權力，強烈要求香港記者證應由香港警務署發出。」<span style=\"color: red;\">更直指記者報道偏頗，應效法歐美做法。</span><br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會其後在FB回應高志森，「<span style=\"color: red;\">你搞錯咗喇！歐盟多國嘅警察唔發記者證，全部都俾工會發。</span>」更解釋到荷蘭和紐約警察有發記者證，因其證可以入埋封鎖線，香港嘅記者證就唔得，又過唔到封鎖線，又防唔到胡椒水。再續：「<span style=\"color: red;\">真正由政府或警察發記者證嘅國家係呢啲：中國內地、北韓、敍利亞、蘇丹、土庫曼斯坦.....詳情可以參考無國界記者網站，CLICK入去全球最冇新聞自由國家名單，就可以搵到。</span>」香港記者協會解釋完後，高志森就將post刪除。<br />\n記協<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1583938/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1583938%2F&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbgEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=d805a103\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1583938%2F&h=47d91c1d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1583938/</a>"},{"pid":"4c88b4c853371bf355107607c0ce41cc276bdf1a","tid":1540776,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b37fd430eeaa704f954f3fccecfa0f14371f9bf","tid":1540776,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b79db980ab01963957afa203082ea408f8f61d3","tid":1540776,"uid":11